HEADWORD: Accuse
<hw>Ac*cuse"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Accusation.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
